"title": "5262: commendation",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5262: commendation",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The act of speaking favourably of someone. Scripture commends those who are faithful and obedient to God.</p>\n<h2>Commendation as speaking favourably of others</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov15:2\">PRO 15:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps145:4\">PSA 145:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:15\">ECC 8:15</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of those commended by God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:10\">MAT 26:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:9\">LUK 7:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:28\">MAT 15:28</a> <em>a Canaanite woman</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:17-Matt16:18\">MAT 16:17–16:18</a> <em>Simon Peter</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:3\">LUK 21:3</a> <em>a poor widow</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:4\">HEB 11:4</a> <em>Abel</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:5\">HEB 11:5</a> <em>Enoch</em></p>\n<h2>Commendation for obedience and faith</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:4\">PSA 40:4</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:1-Heb11:2\">HEB 11:1–11:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:1\">PSA 119:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:20\">PRO 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:2\">ISA 56:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:7\">JER 17:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34\">MAT 25:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:18\">ROM 14:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:18\">2CO 8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:39\">HEB 11:39</a></p>\n<h2>Commendation for perseverance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:18\">ISA 30:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:12\">JAS 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:11\">JAS 5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:19-1Pet2:20\">1PE 2:19–2:20</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of human commendation of others</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam14:25\">2SA 14:25</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor10:18\">2CO 10:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:15\">GEN 12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:8\">GEN 49:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh11:2\">NEH 11:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Esth2:17\">EST 2:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job29:11\">JOB 29:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:8\">PRO 12:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:2\">PRO 27:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:21\">PRO 27:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov28:4\">PRO 28:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:28\">PRO 31:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:30-Prov31:31\">PRO 31:30–31:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:10\">ECC 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song6:9\">SNG 6:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:11\">DAN 10:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:8\">LUK 16:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:41\">JHN 5:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:44\">JHN 5:44</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:43\">JHN 12:43</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:27\">ACT 18:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:28\">ROM 2:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:3\">ROM 13:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:1\">ROM 16:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:2\">1CO 11:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:17\">1CO 11:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:22\">1CO 11:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:1\">2CO 3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:11\">2CO 12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:6\">1TH 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:14\">1PE 2:14</a></p>\n<h2>Self-commendation is to be avoided</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:12\">2CO 5:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:4-2Cor6:10\">2CO 6:4–6:10</a></p>",
